The Tusken Oasis was a nightclub owned by [[Yanth]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]. It was located in [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Crimson Corridor]]. Its amusements included a bar, a [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] quartet, [[Dejarik/Legends|dejarik]] boards, [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]] tables, and dancing girls. It was well-kept, and its decoration included colored lights and statuettes of various mythological beasts.

